A set of scripts to configure servers.


To install on a fresh lenny install:
  wget --no-check-certificate https://github.com/ouvrages/initialize-website/raw/master/lenny/install -O - | bash

On squeeze:
  wget --no-check-certificate https://github.com/ouvrages/initialize-website/raw/master/squeeze/install -O - | bash

On lucid:
  wget https://github.com/ouvrages/initialize-website/raw/master/lucid/install -O - | bash
